content:
Which of the following is not a subfield of anthropology?
A. Linguistic anthropology
B. Socio-cultural anthropology
C. Biological or physical anthropology
D. Archaeological anthropology
E. All of the above are subfields of anthropology

All of the above are subfields of anthropology. Anthropology is a broad field that studies human societies and cultures and their development. It encompasses various subfields, including linguistic anthropology, socio-cultural anthropology, biological or physical anthropology, and archaeological anthropology.因此，正确答案是 E. All of the above are subfields of anthropology.
